13 WHEREAS, the House Agriculture and Consumer Affairs Committee has long recognized
14 the Georgia Farm Bureau Federation under the dedicated leadership of its president, Mr. Tom
15 McCall, as an exemplary voice of Georgia agriculture; and
16 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the Georgia Farm Bureau Federation and
17 its members be appropriately recognized for their many years of dedicated service to Georgia
18 agriculture.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body recognize February 11, 2025, as Georgia Farm Bureau Federation
21 Day at the state capitol.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
23 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
24 Georgia Farm Bureau Federation.
